dc_title_s: Permanent Road Divisions, Nevada County, California, 2020
dc_description_s: Permanent Road Divisions (PRDs) are Dependent Districts that provide enhanced levels of Community services. PRDs might provide road maintenance, and other road related services. Nevada County (Calif.). Geographic Information Services. (2020). Permanent Road Divisions, Nevada County, California, 2020. Nevada County (Calif.). Geographic Information Services. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/fh858pr4292 This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License. This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
